Keller Williams Great Smokies - Bryson City
Mossy Oak Properties Carolina Timber & Realty

data.description: This charming residence is an ideal choice for fulltime homeowners, a relaxing vacation retreat, or a lucrative rental property for savvy investors. Situated just minutes away from Bryson City, the home is conveniently located off 74 West and comes fully furnished. Benefit from a ready-to-use hot tub, private well, straightforward access to main road, a cozy gas fireplace open living/kitchen, split bedroom floorplan, 1 bath and half, large front porch and secluded. Internet connectivity is provided by Frontier. All appliances are included with the property. Seize this chance for a cabin in the mountains. A fantastic opportunity for a profitable rental investment! Sold furnished except for some linens! Check out virtual tour!
